{"type":"message","id":"ad09540f","parentId":"a75262e1","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:33:08.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.exec:19","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"pages\": [\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"mlolson / blender-orchestrator Name Last commit message Last commit date mlolson Replace image links with HTML img tags in README a9dfb32 37 Commits Agentic Blender Orchestrator Create 3D models in Blender using natural language. MCP server lets agent directly control Blender, enabling you to build complex 3D scenes through conversation. Scene comprehension tooling and skills gives LLM improved spatial awareness for better results. Samples created solely with prompts to Claude Opus 4.6 Features 🧠 Spatial Intelligence Suite Spatial intelligence suite helps AI understand space. Natural language positioning — Say \\\"place the lamp on the nightstand\\\" and it figures out the coordinates, checks for collisions, and handles stacking. Real-world dimensions database — 55+ common objects (furniture, appliances, decor) with accurate real-world measurements. The AI knows a kitchen counter is 0.9m tall and a doorway is 2.1m × 0.9m. Collision detection & safe movement — Validate transforms before applying them. Query how far an object can move in each direction without hitting anything. Spatial queries — Ask \\\"what's on the table?\\\" or \\\"what's near the door?\\\" and get answers. Scene Building Guide — A comprehensive reference doc that AI agents can read before building a scene, covering room dimensions, placement rules, common mistakes, and worked examples. 🗺️ Multi-View ASCII Floor Plans ASCII visualizer tool gives the LLM a way to understand spatial relationships between objects. Renders the scene from any angle — top, bottom, front, back, left, right, or all six at once. Configurable resolution up to 120×120 cells. --- Top (looking down, +Z) --- Axes: horizontal=X, vertical=Y | 5.3m x 4.3m (cell: 0.25m, grid: 21x17) WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW W.W W.W W..TTTTTT.W W..TTTTTT.W W..TTTTTT.SS.W WSS.W W.W W.CCCC.W W.CCCC.W W.W WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW Legend: C=Couch, S=Shelf, T=Table, W=Wall_Back\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://github.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n      \"title\": \"GitHub - mlolson/blender-orchestrator: MCP toolset allows agents to control blender. Includes spatial reasoning toolkit for better results.\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/mlolson/blender-orchestrator\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"2 star 2 code issues 88 pull requests discussions actions projects security insights contextlab/orchestrator main 6 branches 0 tags code folders and files name last commit message last commit date latest commit jeremymanning and claude document successful test categories and current progress 278960c · sep 3, 2025 history 756 commits .ccpm_backup issue #248 : core routellm integration with domain router aug 25, 2025 .checkpoints/ test_while_trace test: isolate while loop iteration count issue aug 3, 2025 .claude fix windows ci: replace emojis with ascii text sep 2, 2025 .github/ workflows issue #281 : complete stream d - ci/cd integration &amp; test modes aug 26, 2025 config complete epic merge: complete-refactor sep 2, 2025 data document successful test categories and current progress sep 3, 2025 deep_agents_poc issue #253 : add comprehensive readme for deep agents poc aug 25, 2025 deployment issue #247 : complete production deployment infrastructure aug 25, 2025 docs complete epic merge: complete-refactor sep 2, 2025 examples document successful test categories and current progress sep 3, 2025 notes docs: issue #235 - add completion summary and tracking documentation aug 22, 2025 ops issue #247 : complete production deployment infrastructure aug 25, 2025 pipeline_test_results issue #281 : stream b - quality integration &amp; validation complete aug 26, 2025 production_output issue #263 : production deployment &amp; optimization - epic completion aug 25, 2025 prompts feat: complete issue\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://github.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n      \"title\": \"GitHub - ContextLab/orchestrator: A convenient wrapper for LangGraph, MCP, model spec, and other AI agent control systems\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/ContextLab/orchestrator\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"orchestra mcp插件是一个基于model context protocol的ai项目管理工具包,提供57种内置工具,支持独立cli和集成插件模式,适用于ai助手项目管理和团队协作. go 本地部署\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"Orchestra MCP - AI项目管理协议服务器-MCP服务\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/ad9fb6ac5a8453654e141800ff769114\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"jpicklyk / task-orchestrator Name Last commit message Last commit date jpicklyk Merge pull request #28 from jpicklyk/feature/2.0.0-beta 631fc71 424 Commits\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://github.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n      \"title\": \"GitHub - jpicklyk/task-orchestrator: Persistent AI memory for coding assistants - MCP server providing context persistence across sessions for Claude, Cursor, Windsurf. MCP Tools for task tracking, workflow automation, and AI memory. Eliminates context loss between sessions.\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/jpicklyk/task-orchestrator\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"模型上下文协议 (mcp)是一种协议,你可通过该协议将 github copilot与其他系统集成以扩展其功能. 使用模型上下文协议(mcp)服务器扩展 github copilot的聊天 model context protocol (mcp) is a protocol that allows you to extend the capabilities of github copilot by integrating it with other systems. 设置 github mcp服务器 了解如何配置 github模型上下文协议 (mcp)服务器. 为 github enterprise配置 github mcp服务器 了解如何配置 github模型上下文协议 (mcp)服务器以使用 github enterprise server或具有数据驻留的 github enterprise cloud. 为 github mcp服务器配置工具集 了解如何为 github mcp服务器配置工具集和工具,以便精细控制和优化性能. 使用 github mcp服务器 了解如何使用 github模型上下文协议 (mcp)服务器,直接通过 copilot聊天助手与存储库,议题,拉取请求和其他 github功能进行交互. 在 ide中更改 mcp注册表 自定义可与 copilot聊天助手一起使用的 mcp注册表. 帮助和支持 是否找到了所需的内容? 是 否 仍需帮助? 联系支持人员  legal此内容中的一些内容可能是机器翻译的或 ai 翻译的内容。\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://docs.github.com/apple-touch-icon-precomposed.png\",\n      \"title\": \"使用模型上下文协议 (MCP)\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.github.com/zh/copilot/how-tos/provide-context/use-mcp\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"request_id\": \"bfafdddd-2e35-4ef5-be4e-25ad807590e7\",\n  \"tools\": [],\n  \"status\": 0\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5514,"aggregated":"{\n  \"pages\": [\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"mlolson / blender-orchestrator Name Last commit message Last commit date mlolson Replace image links with HTML img tags in README a9dfb32 37 Commits Agentic Blender Orchestrator Create 3D models in Blender using natural language. MCP server lets agent directly control Blender, enabling you to build complex 3D scenes through conversation. Scene comprehension tooling and skills gives LLM improved spatial awareness for better results. Samples created solely with prompts to Claude Opus 4.6 Features 🧠 Spatial Intelligence Suite Spatial intelligence suite helps AI understand space. Natural language positioning — Say \\\"place the lamp on the nightstand\\\" and it figures out the coordinates, checks for collisions, and handles stacking. Real-world dimensions database — 55+ common objects (furniture, appliances, decor) with accurate real-world measurements. The AI knows a kitchen counter is 0.9m tall and a doorway is 2.1m × 0.9m. Collision detection & safe movement — Validate transforms before applying them. Query how far an object can move in each direction without hitting anything. Spatial queries — Ask \\\"what's on the table?\\\" or \\\"what's near the door?\\\" and get answers. Scene Building Guide — A comprehensive reference doc that AI agents can read before building a scene, covering room dimensions, placement rules, common mistakes, and worked examples. 🗺️ Multi-View ASCII Floor Plans ASCII visualizer tool gives the LLM a way to understand spatial relationships between objects. Renders the scene from any angle — top, bottom, front, back, left, right, or all six at once. Configurable resolution up to 120×120 cells. --- Top (looking down, +Z) --- Axes: horizontal=X, vertical=Y | 5.3m x 4.3m (cell: 0.25m, grid: 21x17) WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW W.W W.W W..TTTTTT.W W..TTTTTT.W W..TTTTTT.SS.W WSS.W W.W W.CCCC.W W.CCCC.W W.W WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW Legend: C=Couch, S=Shelf, T=Table, W=Wall_Back\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://github.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n      \"title\": \"GitHub - mlolson/blender-orchestrator: MCP toolset allows agents to control blender. Includes spatial reasoning toolkit for better results.\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/mlolson/blender-orchestrator\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"2 star 2 code issues 88 pull requests discussions actions projects security insights contextlab/orchestrator main 6 branches 0 tags code folders and files name last commit message last commit date latest commit jeremymanning and claude document successful test categories and current progress 278960c · sep 3, 2025 history 756 commits .ccpm_backup issue #248 : core routellm integration with domain router aug 25, 2025 .checkpoints/ test_while_trace test: isolate while loop iteration count issue aug 3, 2025 .claude fix windows ci: replace emojis with ascii text sep 2, 2025 .github/ workflows issue #281 : complete stream d - ci/cd integration &amp; test modes aug 26, 2025 config complete epic merge: complete-refactor sep 2, 2025 data document successful test categories and current progress sep 3, 2025 deep_agents_poc issue #253 : add comprehensive readme for deep agents poc aug 25, 2025 deployment issue #247 : complete production deployment infrastructure aug 25, 2025 docs complete epic merge: complete-refactor sep 2, 2025 examples document successful test categories and current progress sep 3, 2025 notes docs: issue #235 - add completion summary and tracking documentation aug 22, 2025 ops issue #247 : complete production deployment infrastructure aug 25, 2025 pipeline_test_results issue #281 : stream b - quality integration &amp; validation complete aug 26, 2025 production_output issue #263 : production deployment &amp; optimization - epic completion aug 25, 2025 prompts feat: complete issue\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://github.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n      \"title\": \"GitHub - ContextLab/orchestrator: A convenient wrapper for LangGraph, MCP, model spec, and other AI agent control systems\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/ContextLab/orchestrator\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"orchestra mcp插件是一个基于model context protocol的ai项目管理工具包,提供57种内置工具,支持独立cli和集成插件模式,适用于ai助手项目管理和团队协作. go 本地部署\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"Orchestra MCP - AI项目管理协议服务器-MCP服务\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/ad9fb6ac5a8453654e141800ff769114\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"jpicklyk / task-orchestrator Name Last commit message Last commit date jpicklyk Merge pull request #28 from jpicklyk/feature/2.0.0-beta 631fc71 424 Commits\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://github.com/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n      \"title\": \"GitHub - jpicklyk/task-orchestrator: Persistent AI memory for coding assistants - MCP server providing context persistence across sessions for Claude, Cursor, Windsurf. MCP Tools for task tracking, workflow automation, and AI memory. Eliminates context loss between sessions.\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/jpicklyk/task-orchestrator\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"模型上下文协议 (mcp)是一种协议,你可通过该协议将 github copilot与其他系统集成以扩展其功能. 使用模型上下文协议(mcp)服务器扩展 github copilot的聊天 model context protocol (mcp) is a protocol that allows you to extend the capabilities of github copilot by integrating it with other systems. 设置 github mcp服务器 了解如何配置 github模型上下文协议 (mcp)服务器. 为 github enterprise配置 github mcp服务器 了解如何配置 github模型上下文协议 (mcp)服务器以使用 github enterprise server或具有数据驻留的 github enterprise cloud. 为 github mcp服务器配置工具集 了解如何为 github mcp服务器配置工具集和工具,以便精细控制和优化性能. 使用 github mcp服务器 了解如何使用 github模型上下文协议 (mcp)服务器,直接通过 copilot聊天助手与存储库,议题,拉取请求和其他 github功能进行交互. 在 ide中更改 mcp注册表 自定义可与 copilot聊天助手一起使用的 mcp注册表. 帮助和支持 是否找到了所需的内容? 是 否 仍需帮助? 联系支持人员  legal此内容中的一些内容可能是机器翻译的或 ai 翻译的内容。\",\n      \"hostname\": \"无\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://docs.github.com/apple-touch-icon-precomposed.png\",\n      \"title\": \"使用模型上下文协议 (MCP)\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.github.com/zh/copilot/how-tos/provide-context/use-mcp\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"request_id\": \"bfafdddd-2e35-4ef5-be4e-25ad807590e7\",\n  \"tools\": [],\n  \"status\": 0\n}","cwd":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772249588118}}
